### CCR-017 §5 — Permission Bit Flag RBAC
###
### 검증:
### - JWT payload에 permission 정수 필드
### - None=0, Read=1, Write=2, Delete=4, 조합 가능
### - 리소스별 세분화된 권한 판정

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}
@operator_token = {{$dotenv OPERATOR_JWT}}
@viewer_token = {{$dotenv VIEWER_JWT}}

### 62.1 GET /api/v1/auth/me — JWT payload 확인
GET {{host}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK
# {
#   "sub": "user_01HVQK-admin",
#   "role": "admin",
#   "permission": 7,                    // Read + Write + Delete
#   "assigned_tables": [],              // Admin은 전체 접근
#   "exp": 1743251456
# }

### 62.2 GET /auth/me — Operator
GET {{host}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}

# 예상:
# {
#   "role": "operator",
#   "permission": 3,                    // Read + Write (자기 할당 테이블)
#   "assigned_tables": ["tbl_01", "tbl_05"]
# }

### 62.3 GET /auth/me — Viewer
GET {{host}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상:
# {
#   "role": "viewer",
#   "permission": 1,                    // Read only
#   "assigned_tables": []
# }

### 62.4 PATCH /api/v1/tables/1 — Operator가 자기 할당 테이블 수정 (permission=3)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "name": "Operator updated name"
}

# tbl_01 이 operator_token의 assigned_tables에 포함:
# 예상: 200 OK (permission & Write != 0 + 할당됨)

### 62.5 PATCH /api/v1/tables/99 — Operator가 미할당 테이블
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/tables/99
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "name": "Unauthorized attempt"
}

# tbl_99 는 assigned_tables 에 없음:
# 예상: 403 Forbidden
# {
#   "error": "AUTH_PERMISSION_DENIED",
#   "required_permission": 2,
#   "current_permission": 1,           // 미할당 테이블은 Read only
#   "resource": "tables.99"
# }

### 62.6 DELETE /api/v1/tables/1 — Operator는 Delete 불가
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
If-Match: W/"1-etag"

# 자기 할당이라도 Delete 권한 없음 (permission=3, Delete=4):
# 예상: 403 Forbidden
# { "required_permission": 4, "current_permission": 3 }

### 62.7 PATCH /api/v1/tables/1 — Viewer 거부
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{ "name": "viewer attempt" }

# 예상: 403 Forbidden
# { "required_permission": 2, "current_permission": 1 }

### 62.8 GET /api/v1/tables/1 — Viewer 허용
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK (permission & Read != 0)
